<h2 id='get-credentials'>Get credentials</h2>
<p>To generate API credentials for your test and live environments:</p>

<ol>
<li><p>Log into the <strong>Developer Portal</strong> with your <strong>SmartInventory</strong> account credentials. If you do not have an account, click <strong>Sign Up</strong> to set up an account.</p></li>
<li><p>On <strong>My Web Apps &amp; Credentials</strong>, use the tab to alternate between your <strong>Live</strong> and <strong>Test</strong> web apps.</p></li>
<li><p>Enter a name for your app and click <strong>Create Web App</strong>. </p>

<ul>
<li>Your credentials are displayed on the resulting page. You will need to insert these crendentials into the header of your requests.</li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Review your app information and click <strong>Save</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
